    <x:String x:Key="TxtInitialScanSources">要掃描的來源</x:String>
    <x:String x:Key="TxtInitialScanStart">開始掃描</x:String>
    <x:String x:Key="TxtInitialScanClose">關閉</x:String>
    <x:String x:Key="TxtInitialScanNoDrives">未偵測到磁碟機。</x:String>
